<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 10:08:16 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列军队命名两名在加沙战斗中丧生的预备役军人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-21/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-names-two-reservists-killed-in-gaza-fighting/00000190-3936-d91c-abba-ff36bad30000</link><description>来自加诺·哈达尔（Ganot Hadar）的 25 岁中士奥马尔·斯马德加（Omer Smadga）和来自特拉维夫的 27 岁中士萨迪亚·雅科夫·德里（Saadia Yaakov Dery）在此次事件中丧生，三名预备役军人身受重伤</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 06:31:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-21/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-names-two-reservists-killed-in-gaza-fighting/00000190-3936-d91c-abba-ff36bad30000</guid></item><item><title>从特朗普到本格维尔，愤世嫉俗的破坏者内塔尼亚胡选择了所有错误的一边</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-21/ty-article/.premium/from-trump-to-ben-gvir-netanyahu-the-cynical-saboteur-picks-all-the-wrong-sides/00000190-371f-d6fa-abb4-77bfc96c0000</link><description>干涉美国总统选举后，内塔尼亚胡将自己归为历史错误一边的领导人。 本-格维尔和总理正在进行类似的竞选活动，其中至少有一个让我们想起了我们宁愿做的事情忘记了 ■ 谁嫉妒戈特利夫和萨达的 15 分钟成名？</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 03:08:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-21/ty-article/.premium/from-trump-to-ben-gvir-netanyahu-the-cynical-saboteur-picks-all-the-wrong-sides/00000190-371f-d6fa-abb4-77bfc96c0000</guid></item><item><title>无休止的战争，而不是“全面胜利”：以色列国防军想要离开加沙，但内塔尼亚胡有其他想法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-21/ty-article/.premium/endless-war-not-total-victory-idf-wants-to-leave-gaza-but-netanyahu-has-other-ideas/00000190-368a-d8bc-abf7-b7ba30d00000</link><description>当以色列军队和公众准备结束加沙的战斗，将注意力集中在北部日益激烈的战争时，内塔尼亚胡陷入了他一贯偏执的政治网络中，其中包括琐碎的口号和恶意的指责游戏，他接受了枪击在以色列国防军、抗议者、拜登和所有阻碍他的人</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 03:07:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-21/ty-article/.premium/endless-war-not-total-victory-idf-wants-to-leave-gaza-but-netanyahu-has-other-ideas/00000190-368a-d8bc-abf7-b7ba30d00000</guid></item><item><title>亚美尼亚承认巴勒斯坦国；火箭弹落在加沙边境基布兹</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-21/ty-article-live/blinken-urges-israeli-officials-to-avoid-further-escalation-with-hezbollah/00000190-3888-d49b-a1bd-7bf986180000</link><description>以色列国防军证实击毙了哈马斯无人机操作员；被摧毁的伊斯兰圣战发射场 ■ 美国称，自加沙临时码头重新停泊以来，已经卸载了 656 吨援助物资 ■ 布林肯告诉以色列官员，需要避免与黎巴嫩的局势进一步升级 ■ 以色列国防军在黎巴嫩南部刺杀真主党指挥官 ■ 扎尔的几座房屋被火箭弹直接击中&amp;#39;它，以色列北部</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 02:12:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-21/ty-article-live/blinken-urges-israeli-officials-to-avoid-further-escalation-with-hezbollah/00000190-3888-d49b-a1bd-7bf986180000</guid></item><item><title>以色列公司利用真菌应对气候和土壤危机</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-21/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/the-israeli-company-that-uses-fungus-to-tackle-the-climate-and-soil-crises/00000190-3723-d6fa-abb4-77af14b90000</link><description>一家以色列公司发现了一种通过真菌提高农作物产量的方法。作为一个令人惊奇的、不可预见的好处，添加真菌的土壤吸收的温室气体比地球上最先进的碳捕获系统还要多</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 22:33:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-21/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/the-israeli-company-that-uses-fungus-to-tackle-the-climate-and-soil-crises/00000190-3723-d6fa-abb4-77af14b90000</guid></item><item><title>“广泛且有害”：报告记录了斯坦福大学犹太人的可怕环境</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-06-21/ty-article/.premium/widespread-and-pernicious-report-documents-horrific-environment-for-jews-at-stanford/00000190-379d-d8bc-abf7-b7bf7e430000</link><description>148页报告的作者指责大学官员对“校园反犹太和反以色列言论正常化”“漠不关心”</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 22:00:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-06-21/ty-article/.premium/widespread-and-pernicious-report-documents-horrific-environment-for-jews-at-stanford/00000190-379d-d8bc-abf7-b7bf7e430000</guid></item><item><title>AIPAC vs. Jamaal Bowman：纽约民主党竞选变成对亲以色列团体的公投</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-06-21/ty-article/.premium/aipac-vs-jamaal-bowman-ny-democratic-race-turns-into-referendum-on-pro-israel-group/00000190-34f2-d8bc-abf7-b7f2c3f20000</link><description>AIPAC 已花费超过 1,400 万美元，力图在下周二与挑战者乔治·拉蒂默 (George Latimer) 的竞选中将极左翼民主党人赶下台。作为回应，贾马尔·鲍曼称亲以色列组织为“犹太复国主义政权”，并质疑其针对黑人立法者的目标</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 21:05:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-06-21/ty-article/.premium/aipac-vs-jamaal-bowman-ny-democratic-race-turns-into-referendum-on-pro-israel-group/00000190-34f2-d8bc-abf7-b7f2c3f20000</guid></item><item><title>警察对抗议者的暴行对遭受创伤的以色列人意味着什么</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-20/ty-article/.highlight/what-police-brutality-against-protesters-means-for-israelis-suffering-from-trauma/00000190-3671-d700-a7f0-bff34d3f0000</link><description>以色列充满了未经治疗的创伤，这里的许多人现在都没有参与这场重要的抗议活动，因为他们害怕警察的肮脏行为可能会给他们带来什么，以及他们的反应可能会导致什么</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 20:10:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-20/ty-article/.highlight/what-police-brutality-against-protesters-means-for-israelis-suffering-from-trauma/00000190-3671-d700-a7f0-bff34d3f0000</guid></item><item><title>关于色情、性工作（甚至 Cicciolina）的以色列诗歌会让你心碎</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-06-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israeli-poems-on-porn-sex-work-and-even-cicciolina-that-will-break-your-heart/00000190-3150-d700-a7f0-bdf25c170000</link><description>一本关于卖淫、受害者和嫖客的以色列新诗选，为以色列社会提供了罕见的不同视角</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 18:57:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-06-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israeli-poems-on-porn-sex-work-and-even-cicciolina-that-will-break-your-heart/00000190-3150-d700-a7f0-bdf25c170000</guid></item><item><title>报告：以色列军队无视观察员关于哈马斯在 10 月 7 日之前在边境附近举行“不寻常”训练的警告</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-20/ty-article/idf-ignored-warning-by-army-spotter-that-hamas-held-unusual-training-days-before-oct-7/00000190-36e0-d6fa-abb4-77ef0c840000</link><description>据以色列公共广播公司 Kan 11 报道，观察员报道称，大约 170 名哈马斯特工正在训练如何在攻击以色列坦克兵的同时发射火箭，这一例行程序于四天后（即 10 月 7 日）实施</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 18:46:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-20/ty-article/idf-ignored-warning-by-army-spotter-that-hamas-held-unusual-training-days-before-oct-7/00000190-36e0-d6fa-abb4-77ef0c840000</guid></item><item><title>白宫炮轰攻击拜登的视频“令人失望”，内塔尼亚胡谴责“人身攻击”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-06-20/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-decries-personal-attacks-as-white-house-blasts-disappointing-video/00000190-36ab-de3a-a19a-f6abd2180000</link><description>国家安全委员会发言人约翰·柯比为拜登政府辩护，反对内塔尼亚胡公开指责其推迟向以色列运送武器。共和党参议员汤姆·科顿也加入了对内塔尼亚胡的攻击，称白宫的行为是“官僚花招”</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 18:24:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-06-20/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-decries-personal-attacks-as-white-house-blasts-disappointing-video/00000190-36ab-de3a-a19a-f6abd2180000</guid></item><item><title>正统派和以色列极端民族主义者之间的婚姻是否开始破裂？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-06-20/ty-article/.premium/is-the-marriage-between-haredim-and-israeli-ultranationalists-beginning-to-break-up/00000190-3644-de3a-a19a-f6646ba00000</link><description>三十年前，极端正统的沙斯党加入了支持和平的左翼政府。但随后正统派政党急剧转向政治极右翼，内塔尼亚胡掌权数十年。但现在出现了重大转变的初步迹象</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 17:48:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-06-20/ty-article/.premium/is-the-marriage-between-haredim-and-israeli-ultranationalists-beginning-to-break-up/00000190-3644-de3a-a19a-f6646ba00000</guid></item><item><title>BDS 将贾斯汀·比伯和拉娜·德雷列入黑名单后，“犹太复国主义”作家又成为攻击目标</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-06-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/after-blacklisting-justin-bieber-and-lana-del-rey-its-zionist-authors-turn/00000190-365b-d700-a7f0-bffb798c0000</link><description>世界各地的作家都被列入了一份名为“你最喜欢的作家是犹太复国主义者吗？”的病毒名单上的黑名单。诸如参加哈达萨读书俱乐部或称哈马斯 10 月 7 日的行为“不可接受”等“罪行”。抵制他们作品的呼吁效果如何？谁受到的伤害最大？</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 17:47:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-06-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/after-blacklisting-justin-bieber-and-lana-del-rey-its-zionist-authors-turn/00000190-365b-d700-a7f0-bffb798c0000</guid></item><item><title>“这不是你在美国看到的”：犹太说唱歌手兼喜剧演员科沙·迪尔兹在以色列反政府抗议中看到了什么</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-06-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/what-jewish-rapper-comedian-kosha-dillz-saw-at-an-israeli-anti-government-protest/00000190-3590-d8bc-abf7-b7b25d9c0000</link><description>Kosha Dillz（又名 Rami Even-Esh）自 10 月 7 日以来第四次访问以色列，在特拉维夫一家挤满人的俱乐部表演，但在此之前他曾参加过一场反政府抗议活动。在参加美国支持巴勒斯坦和支持以色列的集会几个月后，他相信自己拥有“很多人没有的观点”</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 17:46:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-06-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/what-jewish-rapper-comedian-kosha-dillz-saw-at-an-israeli-anti-government-protest/00000190-3590-d8bc-abf7-b7b25d9c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 258 天：官员称，如果巴解组织不统治加沙，内战将爆发</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-20/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-258-civil-war-will-erupt-in-gaza-if-plo-doesnt-rule-it-official-says/00000190-367d-d690-a190-f6ff3d700001</link><description>据《华尔街日报》报道，加沙地带可能只有 50 名活着的以色列人质 ■ 真主党向以色列北部发射了约 25 枚火箭 ■ 巴解组织高级官员称，如果巴解组织不控制加沙，内战将在加沙爆发 ■ 以色列对战争造成的伤亡还没有做好准备以色列电力管理公司首席执行官表示，与真主党合作将对其电网造成影响 ■以下是战争进入 258 天后您需要了解的信息</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 16:55:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-20/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-258-civil-war-will-erupt-in-gaza-if-plo-doesnt-rule-it-official-says/00000190-367d-d690-a190-f6ff3d700001</guid></item><item><title>德国以反犹太主义为由将 BDS 指定为“可疑的极端主义组织”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-06-20/ty-article/.premium/germany-designates-bds-as-suspected-extremist-group-citing-antisemitism-concerns/00000190-361d-d700-a7f0-bfffd7250000</link><description>该指定允许德国当局监视 BDS 活动人士并在该组织内招募线人。德国引用了 BDS 宪章中的极端主义证据，该宪章呼吁“解放所有阿拉伯土地”，以及它从哈马斯获得的支持</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 16:41:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-06-20/ty-article/.premium/germany-designates-bds-as-suspected-extremist-group-citing-antisemitism-concerns/00000190-361d-d700-a7f0-bfffd7250000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警察法律顾问：警察不能在抗议活动中没收标语</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-20/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-legal-advisor-police-officers-cannot-confiscate-signs-at-protests/00000190-35e6-d8bc-abf7-b7f6848b0000</link><description>这些命令是在警察暴力没收抗议者标有反政府和战争口号的标语后向以色列高等法院提出请愿书后公布的。尽管如此，在没有法律授权的情况下，没收标志的行为仍在继续</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 15:58:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-20/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-legal-advisor-police-officers-cannot-confiscate-signs-at-protests/00000190-35e6-d8bc-abf7-b7f6848b0000</guid></item><item><title>面对与真主党迫在眉睫的战争，以色列有六个艰难的选择</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-06-20/ty-article-opinion/.premium/facing-a-looming-war-with-hezbollah-israel-has-six-tough-options/00000190-3434-d5f5-a5d6-fdfead7f0000</link><description>以色列正在应对与加沙哈马斯和胆大妄为的伊朗持续交战的前所未有的局势，同时决定如何应对与黎巴嫩真主党不断升级的跨境战斗。它的下一步行动必须以最经过计算和校准的方式完成——没有犯错的余地</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 15:55:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-06-20/ty-article-opinion/.premium/facing-a-looming-war-with-hezbollah-israel-has-six-tough-options/00000190-3434-d5f5-a5d6-fdfead7f0000</guid></item><item><title>日本规模较小：以色列为何决定在 2025 年世博会上低调亮相</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/why-israel-decided-to-lower-its-profile-at-expo-2025-in-osaka/00000190-2b43-d39e-a999-7fcf103b0000</link><description>世博会没有在显眼位置建造豪华展馆，而是在边缘选择了一个小得多的替代方案。 “在我看来，最好不要参与，”提交了原始提案之一的建筑师大卫·克纳福 (David Knafo) 说道。</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 15:55:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/why-israel-decided-to-lower-its-profile-at-expo-2025-in-osaka/00000190-2b43-d39e-a999-7fcf103b0000</guid></item><item><title>“以色列有两张脸”：他们逃离俄罗斯，却发现以色列有多相似</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/leisure/2024-06-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-has-two-faces-they-escaped-russia-only-to-discover-how-similar-israel-is/00000190-2bf9-d39e-a999-7ffffa300000</link><description>乌克兰入侵后，艺术家维罗妮卡和丹尼尔·伯纳德从俄罗斯移居以色列。这里的生活是他们意想不到的一切：“我们正在努力保持理智和批判性思维”</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 15:42:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/leisure/2024-06-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-has-two-faces-they-escaped-russia-only-to-discover-how-similar-israel-is/00000190-2bf9-d39e-a999-7ffffa300000</guid></item></channel></rss>